 camping. Like I said... good luck =) <p><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81496">Dolalin</a> Bonewielder<br>Warlock of The Shadow Order<br>Lanys T`Vyl</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uvenen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Venen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardaholic</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/10/02 6:45:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=552.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.crocker.com/~denise/amflag.gif  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Guide to soloing Verix Kylox room in KC</span><hr size=1> Or use Dire charm and let your pet solo it =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.showPrevMessage?topicID=552.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.showNextMessage?topicID=552.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=552.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.emailToFriend?topicID=552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecromancer.threadControl?topicID=552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumnecroma